The paper discusses the generation of adversarial perturbations, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). The use of adaptive gradient methods is also a common technique in optimization and deep learning (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper discusses the security implications of adversarial attacks, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR).
